        <p class="font-sora text-green text-[15px] font-semibold leading-relaxed mb-5" style="max-width:70ch;">Plan on $825–$2,000 in first-year costs on top of the purchase price: a large cage, perches and toys, an initial avian vet visit, a year of food, and enrichment.</p>
