          <p>Two notes on the recurring lines. Food matters more in a Grey than in almost any other parrot — the species is prone to calcium deficiency, and a dye-free formulated pellet base with fresh greens is the foundation; our <a href="/best-african-grey-parrot-food/">best African Grey food guide</a> walks through exactly what to buy and what that $200–$400 actually purchases.</p>
