          <p>Toys and perches — not because they matter less, but because Greys destroy them on schedule anyway. Untreated bird-safe wood, stainless hardware, and a rotation of a few toys at a time deliver the same enrichment as a $400 toy haul.</p>
          <h4 class="font-sora font-bold text-[13px] uppercase tracking-wide text-clay-ink mt-3 mb-1">Where Should You Never Trim It?</h4>
